{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Even when they took us out to the train, she held onto this bundle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "In case she died, she wanted to be buried in the [NON-ENGLISH], in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And they-- people were dying in the train, too, because there was no room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "It was-- everybody was jammed in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And there were fights breaking out-- people didn't get along.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Because, you know, to stay crammed up like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Every-- [SIGHS] And then they closed the doors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They closed the doors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "There were two sliding doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Or one sliding door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "They closed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And in the top there was a little window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "The window must have been maybe about-- about maybe 12, 14 inches.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Maybe about 20 inches or 2 feet long by 12, 14 inches high.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And under the window there was barbed wire, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And I was near the window and I would sometimes pull myself up and look out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "You know, I could look out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we left [NON-ENGLISH], that-- I would say, around 1 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we arrived midnight to a place called Kosice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Kosice, this is what it's called in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Today it's partly-- today it's the second largest city in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But in Hungarian it was called Kassa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "All the trains from Hungary going to Auschwitz went through Kassa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And again, that-- the middle of the night, we heard in Hungarian, first, anybody has jewelry, money, silverware has to get rid of what.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "If anybody is caught with it is going to be shot forthwith.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And about 15 minutes later we heard the same story-- anybody with jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "But this time, it wasn't spoken in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "This time it was spoken in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And the Germans took over in Kosice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "They took over the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
